%^YELLOW%^Skill: Stealth

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's stealth skill indicates their aptitude at moving while unseen and unheard. It affects abilities that involve hiding within one's surroundings, and a thief's ability to move into a position unnoticed in order to stab an opponent.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^dexterity
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^sneaking, hide in shadows, stab

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Related helpfiles: %^WHITE%^skills, sneak, hide in shadows, stab
